Benue – Nigerians on social media have been battling to hold back their tears since the news of a family perishing in an accident surfaced. Here is a heartbreaking burial poster of Benue lady and her three kids who died in accident. They will be buried today September 18, 2019.May their souls. The trio were heading out when their vehicle was involved in a fatal road accident and they died. Since this poster surfaced, Nigerians have become so prayerful about the acclaimed evils of the ’ember month’. The names of the deceased have been given as Mrs. Ngumimi Comfort Jebe, Jebe David Jnr, Jebe Iwueseter Beauty, Jebe Favour Muthie Dooshima. Source